OL,3,CNew buy now, pay later rules - what do
OL,4,Cthey mean for you?
OL,6,FBuy now, pay later customers have been
OL,7,Fgiven a range of new protections under
OL,8,Freforms that have now come into force.
OL,10,FFrom Wednesday, the sector has come
OL,11,Funder the regulation of the Financial
OL,12,FConduct Authority (FCA), and lenders
OL,13,Fwill need to be authorised by the
OL,14,Fregulator to provide Buy now, pay
OL,15,Flater (BNPL) products.
OL,17,FBNPL firms will also be subject to the
OL,18,FConsumer Duty, which requires
OL,19,Ffinancial firms to put customers at
OL,20,Fthe heart of what they do and which is
OL,21,Foverseen by the FCA.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
