OL,3,CNew buy now, pay later rules - what do
OL,4,Cthey mean for you?
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the FCA said: "Buy
OL,7,Fnow pay later can be a form of credit,
OL,8,Fbut people deserve to be protected
OL,9,Fwhen using it.
OL,11,F"Lenders should check their customers
OL,12,Fcan afford to pay it back."
OL,14,FHere is how the changes could affect
OL,15,Fyou.
OL,17,FHow does BNPL work?
OL,26,@nD@bOUsD@AOUtD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
