OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784168292
OL,3,CNew buy now, pay later rules - what do
OL,4,Cthey mean for you?
OL,6,FBNPL options, like Klarna and
OL,7,FClearpay, often appear at online
OL,8,Fcheckouts, allowing shoppers to spread
OL,9,Fthe cost of their purchase without
OL,10,Fpaying interest, rather than making a
OL,11,Fpayment all in one go.
OL,13,FWhy has BNPL been controversial?
OL,15,FFor many people, using BNPL will ease
OL,16,Fcost pressures by spreading payments
OL,17,Finto more palatable chunks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784168292
OL,3,CNew buy now, pay later rules - what do
OL,4,Cthey mean for you?
OL,6,FResponsible spenders can use BNPL
OL,7,Feffectively, but some have been
OL,8,Ftempted to stretch their finances too
OL,9,Ffar.
OL,11,FThis could also mean some people
OL,12,Fturning to debt, which incurs charges,
OL,13,Fsuch as overdrafts, to cover the cost
OL,14,Fof their BNPL debt.
OL,16,FBusinesses and banks that offer loans
OL,17,Fhave, in the past, been under FCA
OL,18,Fregulation to ensure that the people
OL,19,Fthey lend to can pay back what they
OL,20,Fborrow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784168292
OL,3,CNew buy now, pay later rules - what do
OL,4,Cthey mean for you?
OL,6,FBut the relatively new BNPL, despite
OL,7,Feffectively offering a loan, has not
OL,8,Fbeen under similar regulation until
OL,9,Fnow.
OL,11,FWhat are the key changes?
OL,13,FThe sector will be overseen by the FCA
OL,14,Fand subject to its regulation.
OL,16,FThis means firms will be required to
OL,17,Fgive customers clear, upfront details
OL,18,Fabout their agreement, including when
OL,19,Fpayments are due, amounts, and what
OL,20,Fhappens if they miss a payment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784168292
OL,3,CNew buy now, pay later rules - what do
OL,4,Cthey mean for you?
OL,6,FLenders must carry out proportionate
OL,7,Fchecks to ensure customers can afford
OL,8,Fto repay what they borrow before
OL,9,Foffering BNPL.
OL,11,FPeople may find that their BNPL use is
OL,12,Ftaken into account by lenders using
OL,13,Fcredit reports to make future lending
OL,14,Fdecisions ` which may have a positive
OL,15,For negative impact depending on the
OL,16,Fborrower's financial behaviour.
OL,18,FFirms will need to offer support to
OL,19,Fcustomers in financial difficulty and,
OL,20,Fwhere appropriate, direct them to free
OL,21,Fdebt advice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784168292
OL,3,CNew buy now, pay later rules - what do
OL,4,Cthey mean for you?
OL,6,FSome BNPL providers have said they
OL,7,Falready offer strong protections for
OL,8,Fconsumers and have welcomed regulation
OL,9,Fas a way of levelling the playing
OL,10,Ffield.
OL,12,FWhat if I want to complain?
OL,14,FBNPL customers will now have the
OL,15,Foption to complain to the Financial
OL,16,FOmbudsman Service (FOS) if they wish
OL,17,Fto, for example, if they are unhappy
OL,18,Fwith the affordability of the
OL,19,Fagreement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784168292
OL,3,CNew buy now, pay later rules - what do
OL,4,Cthey mean for you?
OL,6,FThe ombudsman service settles disputes
OL,7,Fbetween consumers and regulated
OL,8,Ffinancial businesses and is free for
OL,9,Fconsumers to use themselves directly.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FConsumers will be able to take a
OL,17,Fcomplaint to the ombudsman as long as
OL,18,Fthe complaint is about agreements
OL,19,Ftaken out on or after July 15 2026,
OL,20,Fand the complaint is about a regulated
OL,21,Ffirm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784168292
OL,3,CNew buy now, pay later rules - what do
OL,4,Cthey mean for you?
OL,6,FCustomers will need to complain to
OL,7,Ftheir BNPL provider first, and if they
OL,8,Fare unhappy with the response, they
OL,9,Fcan submit a complaint to the FOS.
OL,11,FWhat if I am worried about debts?
OL,13,FBuy now, pay later may make it more
OL,14,Ftempting to make more purchases or
OL,15,Fspend more than initially budgeted
OL,16,Ffor, but charity StepChange suggests
OL,17,Fpausing to consider whether you would
OL,18,Fstill be buying the items in the first
OL,19,Fplace if they were not available on
OL,20,Fcredit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
