PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784168292
OL,3,CNew buy now, pay later rules - what do
OL,4,Cthey mean for you?
OL,6,FThe charity also suggests keeping a
OL,7,Fnote of payments and the terms of each
OL,8,Floan agreement to make sure this fits
OL,9,Fwith your budget and that you will not
OL,10,Fhave to cut back on essentials.
OL,12,FThis could be particularly helpful for
OL,13,Fpeople with multiple debts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
