OL,3,CNew buy now, pay later rules - what do
OL,4,Cthey mean for you?
OL,6,FPeople who are struggling with loans
OL,7,Fshould contact their lender, and
OL,8,Fsupport is also available from various
OL,9,Forganisations, such as StepChange,
OL,10,FCitizens Advice, Christians Against
OL,11,FPoverty and the National Debtline debt
OL,12,Fadvice service run by the Money Advice
OL,13,FTrust.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
